國highway踩到去100英哩來回Manchester同London<br />\n<br />\n係澳洲半夜行highway無街燈前後無車，漆黑一片，唯一光源係自己車頭燈，仲踩住百三四咁去，好撚刺激"},{"pid":"351c157a75fef154a07d42ff7ab8d2216f7c7981","tid":500652,"uid":83097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:01:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有呀<br />\n不過我正係試過越南，泰國同緬甸<br />\n咁樣算唔算</blockquote><br />\n點解唔算<br />\n三個國家自由行? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"395641da301c73ae065a31f88b3a899332712a08","tid":500652,"uid":83097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:01:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>英國，澳洲<br />\n<br />\n係英國highway踩到去100英哩來回Manchester同London<br />\n<br />\n係澳洲半夜行highway無街燈前後無車，漆黑一片，唯一光源係自己車頭燈，仲踩住百三四咁去，好撚刺激</blockquote><br />\n葡萄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但驚唔驚炒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33bc096f41022d8ac1584157964b167e3008d29e","tid":500652,"uid":102338,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T08:10:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>英國，澳洲<br />\n<br />\n係英國highway踩到去100英哩來回Manchester同London<br />\n<br />\n係澳洲半夜行highway無街燈前後無車，漆黑一片，唯一光源係自己車頭燈，仲踩住百三四咁去，好撚刺激</blockquote><br />\n葡萄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但驚唔驚炒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n少少,不過我對自己手車有信心,最重要係眼訓千祈唔好繼續渣,一定要搵地方停低休息"},{"pid":"aa798483f07677cfc09c9f2ad0283d28eb83aa41","tid":500652,"uid":71524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T10:02:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有呀<br />\n不過我正係試過越南，泰國同緬甸<br />\n咁樣算唔算</blockquote><br />\n點解唔算<br />\n三個國家自由行? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀<br />\n正係試過係緬甸蕩失路其他都冇咩"},{"pid":"68c5cd96f0f878191dbaf255266e51d02059ce49","tid":500652,"uid":71524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T10:06:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有呀<br />\n不過我正係試過越南，泰國同緬甸<br />\n咁樣算唔算</blockquote><br />\n點解唔算<br />\n三個國家自由行? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀<br />\n正係試過係緬甸蕩失路其他都冇咩<br />\n係泰國就試過落大雨咁係曼谷落華欣個陣，前面部16噸係到打白鴿，好彩我停得切，不過好多大直路都唔覺意咁開到160km/h咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"026810bf2863e95359b266ac6e23751b402bf731","tid":500652,"uid":1066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T10:10:36.000Z","msg":"做過 唔建議<br />\n一個人自己好快悶 <br />\n之前係美國渣 悶加眼訓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後變左迫自己渣車（好似返工禁）<br />\n攪到最後有d 地方想去 都無去 ,急急地 直接番屋企"},{"pid":"11bf2a548bbe15a0c91b939bfb2c29d3d1c1b724","tid":500652,"uid":131670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T10:24:46.000Z","msg":"10日去左美東5個城市"},{"pid":"3d8b57afa1f59751f89a2b13ff200ca5b964eae5","tid":500652,"uid":33566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T10:26:21.000Z","msg":"係NZ十日都係自己一個揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時去日本郊外地區都會自己一個揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最緊要一樣野係，你平時有無揸開車<br />\n你係香港既駕駛環境生存到，去到外國你會覺得d人真係好撚有禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d1158545ba453d1a3218349ecebb51e00076e4","tid":500652,"uid":67771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T13:42:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>英國，澳洲<br />\n<br />\n係英國highway踩到去100英哩來回Manchester同London<br />\n<br />\n係澳洲半夜行highway無街燈前後無車，漆黑一片，唯一光源係自己車頭燈，仲踩住百三四咁去，好撚刺激</blockquote><br />\n葡萄 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但驚唔驚炒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n少少,不過我對自己手車有信心,最重要係眼訓千祈唔好繼續渣,一定要搵地方停低休息</blockquote><br />\n上次日本趕番民宿, 都係無街燈前後無車，漆黑一片山路踩80, 反而第二朝日光日白行6~70<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e21f499d568618e030bf57d6191b2078644691","tid":500652,"uid":113144,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T13:48:43.000Z","msg":"濟洲試過 <br />\n花蓮就仲癲 渣電單車（但本身無牌）不過架電單車都好慢 快極都係60mk/h..<br />\n黎緊台中/台南都想偷雞渣下電單車<br />\n<br />\n好鐘意自己渣車 播住自己鐘意既歌 開自己既演唱會"},{"pid":"d23e583aeeadaf8d321b55e64af1df8d8784ee29","tid":500652,"uid":7674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T13:54:13.000Z","msg":"德國，揸200都比人放到無星星"},{"pid":"ceb84835ca233c601149e81276828377dee44bc7","tid":500652,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T15:07:27.000Z","msg":"試過台灣3日揸左1000公里"},{"pid":"d0836e14efcb9dc98187e845d138cbe8f5d28212","tid":500652,"uid":147183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T12:01:41.000Z","msg":"差唔多日日都係<br />\n利申外國JJ"}]}